(lectotype, designated by 
<bibRefCitation id="D98CD0AD2818F844ED65689A1F685C55" author="Craven, LA" journalOrPublisher="Australian Systematic Botany" pageId="10" pageNumber="111" pagination="521 - 657" publicationUrl="10.1071/SB9960521" refId="B8" refString="Craven, LA, 1996. A taxonomic revision of Heliotropium (Boraginaceae) in Australia. Australian Systematic Botany 9 (4): 521 - 657, DOI: 10.1071/SB9960521" title="A taxonomic revision of Heliotropium (Boraginaceae) in Australia." url="10.1071/SB9960521" volume="9" year="1996">Craven 1996</bibRefCitation>
